{"id": 2503, "genre": 1001, "title": "和上一代人相比，你觉得本届年轻人都有哪些糟心的窘境?", "description": "「上啃老下无小没兄弟姐妹，靠猫星人来延续后代」的一代。", "record_count": 5919, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180830085252uDblq6t70NoIMRCp.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-07T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 297728, "content": "空有鸿鹄之志，手无缚鸡之力\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672964}, {"id": 300544, "content": "结婚难，单身太多了😄", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1453058}, {"id": 297729, "content": "混吃等死，还没有梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243653}, {"id": 297985, "content": "到处都是灌鸡汤的人，其实是最没营养的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423837}, {"id": 297730, "content": "出生在最好的时代，却没赶上这个最好的时代。", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429931}, {"id": 297731, "content": "意识形态很奇怪，跟你谈社会主义、共产主义、个人奋斗的人都很富有", "image": null, "praise_count": 126, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386627}, {"id": 297732, "content": "不知道互联网的出现让对社会，时代了解更多，更深，才会觉得这个现状很糟", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1249913}, {"id": 297733, "content": "中等收入陷阱...", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428369}, {"id": 297734, "content": "只有生活，没有梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417999}, {"id": 297736, "content": "这个看脸的社会，爱豆画风都突变，学生们的审美也很扭曲？", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963953}, {"id": 297737, "content": "几代人努力换来一套房，后面请帮我接上，我没力气说下去了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244139}, {"id": 297993, "content": "还不错吧", "image": "img/option/option/20180909225849JhsEu4nRDjH1mxcV", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609598}, {"id": 297738, "content": "贫富差距大 导致的心态失衡。。上一代是大部分都穷得安心，这一代是一比较 总有更富的人。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227251}, {"id": 297739, "content": "逐渐稳定的社会等级，和自身力量的渺小", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1326291}, {"id": 297995, "content": "爱情是不是要走向婚姻\n婚姻走向长久的可能性有多大\n婚姻制度有没有可能转变为如同公司签约一样的制度\n就算结婚生娃，将来与孩子互相不喜欢怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 297740, "content": "畸形放假套住了年轻人的梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433552}, {"id": 297997, "content": "面对更加多元化的世界，再也不是一板一眼简单的过了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1436650}, {"id": 297742, "content": "婚姻如交易，结不起，谈不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320277}, {"id": 298254, "content": "孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023268}, {"id": 297743, "content": "日常焦绿", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433558}, {"id": 297744, "content": "容易懈怠，容易抑郁", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178586}, {"id": 298000, "content": "不想活，又不敢死", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1436798}, {"id": 297745, "content": "伪国际化，感觉经济开放了但文化退后了", "image": null, "praise_count": 307, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311434}, {"id": 298001, "content": "每天都会看的杂志突然就停刊了一个月", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254189}, {"id": 297747, "content": "贫富差距太大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746493}, {"id": 297748, "content": "现实和理想冲突、机遇和挑战并存、生与死的面对", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415153}, {"id": 297749, "content": "想要太多付出太少", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433599}, {"id": 297751, "content": "能力承担不起梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433643}, {"id": 298776, "content": "佛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441331}, {"id": 297753, "content": "对周围的事情漠不关心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433670}, {"id": 297754, "content": "一腔热血的时候，人微言轻；\n三五年后，思维能力犹如一潭死水。\n焦虑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433665}, {"id": 297755, "content": "我思考的越多想的越明白 就活的越不开心 拿婚姻举例我越是知道自己想要的是什么越找不到可以结婚的对象也越不敢结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433676}, {"id": 297756, "content": "不求稳定，但求随心！", "image": "img/option/option/20180907162506n5zR3ldg9fQBtckj", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 297757, "content": "活不活都无所谓，现在在这里只是为了家人而活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1402186}, {"id": 297759, "content": "喜欢单身就要选择性耳聋。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911878}, {"id": 297760, "content": "单身的担心收单身税\n结婚的担心叫二胎基金🤷🏻‍♀️", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254456}, {"id": 297761, "content": "老一辈很多封建思想我很不喜欢。比如:谈性色变，把生育当目的，把无知当纯洁，把愚昧当德行，把偏见当原则。", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1432057}, {"id": 297762, "content": "可能在后年被消灭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714457}, {"id": 297763, "content": "老一辈希望的工作稳定，与当前社会的不进则退", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1432774}, {"id": 297764, "content": "孤单又热闹", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397575}, {"id": 299300, "content": "阶级固化。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279123}, {"id": 297765, "content": "放假回家，突然多了个妹妹or弟弟", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1433708}, {"id": 297766, "content": "其实吧，就是30多了还没有长大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429862}, {"id": 297767, "content": "竞争激烈 三十岁需满足的东西太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381307}, {"id": 297768, "content": "社保交的越来越多，退休年龄却越来越退后。\n结果就是我们这一代价的社保只不过是为了养活上一代没有交社保的人。而我们很多人的父母并没有退休金。", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380156}, {"id": 297769, "content": "死不了，活不旺", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375910}, {"id": 297770, "content": "习惯于用自嘲来掩饰自己的不足，奢望一笑了之，却不愿意做丝毫的改变。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434070}, {"id": 297771, "content": "房价绑架了幸福感和可能性", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955985}, {"id": 298795, "content": "找对象难，找到理想工作难，信任别人难", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1432262}, {"id": 297774, "content": "了解真实的近代史成为有生之年系列", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354722}]}